<p><strong>Bug B</strong> — The stand should be <strong>hollow inside</strong> so you can stand a shopkeeper in it. But the whole stand comes out as a <strong>solid block</strong> of bricks you cannot enter.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">def build_stall(stand, post, roof, x1, x2, z1, z2):
    blocks.fill(stand, pos(x1, 0, z1), pos(x2, 0, z2), FillOperation.REPLACE)

build_stall(BRICKS, OAK_FENCE, BRICKS, 2, 10, 2, 6)
</code></pre>
